{"type":"text","timestamp":1775834029357,"sessionID":"ses_2880bb8eeffe61cXJno4eNibiH","part":{"id":"prt_d77f4bee1001612PcgbFakfD4I","messageID":"msg_d77f4965e001y8jl1OXXNnV5Y3","sessionID":"ses_2880bb8eeffe61cXJno4eNibiH","type":"text","text":"**AR-012 — 会话存储接口定义 — Archive Summary**\n\n---\n\n**Completed:**\n\n| Area | Details |\n|---|---|\n| **Store interface** | `pkg/store/store.go` — 11-method `Store` interface: CRUD (Store/Update/Delete/Get/List Sandbox), activity tracking (UpdateSessionLastActivity), cleanup queries (ListExpired/InactiveSandboxes), lifecycle (Ping, Close) |\n| **Redis impl** | `store_redis.go` — full implementation using `go-redis/v9`, pipelined writes for Store/Delete, ZSET-based expiry & activity indexes |\n| **Valkey impl** | `store_valkey.go` — full implementation using `valkey-go`, supports cluster/single, cache toggle, env-driven config |\n| **Codec** | `codec.go` — JSON marshal/unmarshal for `SandboxInfo` |\n| **Singleton** | `singleton.go` — `sync.Once` init, `STORE_TYPE` env switch (`redis` default, `valkey`) |\n| **Tests** | 45 tests total: Redis (21, with miniredis), Valkey (16, validation-only), Codec (5), Singleton (3) |\n\n**Deferred:**\n\n| Area | Details |\n|---|---|\n| **Valkey integration tests** | No live Valkey server tests — only input validation and struct tests; Redis has miniredis but Valkey has no equivalent mock |\n| **UpdateSandbox index sync** | `UpdateSandbox` updates the main key but does **not** refresh the expiry/activity ZSET scores (stale index risk) |\n| **Key-level TTL** | Session keys are stored without Redis `EXPIRE` — relies solely on ZSET indexes for cleanup, no automatic key eviction |\n| **Memory store** | No in-memory fallback implementation for local/dev use |\n| **Pagination** | `ListSandboxes` returns all entries — no offset/limit support for large datasets |","time":{"start":1775834029355,"end":1775834029355}}}
